x4freetext: English translation
The tritons produced in a thin target were
caught by stacks of aluminum foil situated at a
distance of 15 cm from the target at different angles
in the range 7-150 degr. After irradiation tritium
was extracted from the foils by means of heating and
was introduced into a Geiger counter.
